      "description": "FEA-predicted yield force compared to experimental mean. Percent difference 6.1%; E/uval = 1.31 (< 1.96). Acceptance criterion met."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/nagaraja-cou1-vr-force40mm",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Force at 40 mm displacement QoI comparison — FEA vs. experimental (N=11)",
      "description": "FEA-predicted force at 40 mm displacement compared to experimental mean. Percent difference 7.8%; E/uval = 1.61 (< 1.96). Acceptance criterion met."
    }
  ],
